# Thursday Night Color Scheme

Dark color scheme for Atom based on Tomorrow Night.

![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Dnld/atom-thursday-night-syntax/master/screenshots/thursday-night-screenshot.png)

### Colors

```
text: #BABABA;
background: #2B2C2F;
selection: #3E4043;
comment: #555557;
cursor: #81a2be;
red: #cc6666;
orange: #de935f;
yellow: #f0c674;
green: #99C794;
aqua: #9ac9c4;
blue: #81a2be;
purple: #b294bb;
```
